data.description: This simply breathtaking all brick and stucco exterior home is located on 8 acres in a gated community in beautiful Perry, GA. The home’s elegance and thoughtful touches make it the entertainer’s dream. Built in 2016, the home boasts a stunning 5 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms, a theater room, and 4,321 sq. ft.   When you arrive at 1004 Eagle Feather Drive, you are greeted by a long driveway, custom brick entryway columns, and palm trees, making you and your guests feel transported to an oasis. As you step through the gorgeous wood stained double doors into the grand foyer you are welcomed by a stunning chandelier and marble flooring. As you continue into the open concept home you will see the formal dining room and a sitting room or office. As you walk into the connected living room and kitchen, you see the home is bright and welcoming with lots of natural light. The centerpiece of the spacious living room is the gorgeous stacked stone fireplace. The kitchen has beautiful custom cabinetry, a gas cooktop, bar seating, an eat-in kitchen area, a beautiful backsplash, and stainless steel appliances throughout. The home boasts a spacious laundry room with custom cabinetry for storage.   Each of the five bedrooms have light and bright carpet flooring for peak comfort and each full bathroom has custom cabinetry and jetted bathtubs. The Master Suite is extremely spacious and boasts its own double-sided gas fireplace in the master bedroom and bathroom. The master suite has an extra room attached that can be used as a bonus private sitting area. The serene jetted bathtub and beautiful tile shower will transport you to peak relaxation. The theater room brings a fun and unique element to this home. From enjoying sporting events or family movie nights in your home, the possibilities are endless.   Taking a step out the back door of this home, you see the gorgeous pool with a rod iron fence surrounding and the ultimate outdoor hosting pavilion. The griller’s dream cooking area boasts its own refrigerator, built-in charcoal grill and flattop grill, plenty of counter space, a sink, and storage. This is a great entertaining space for large gatherings of family and friends poolside. The home has an attached two car garage.   This home is waiting for you! Schedule your private showing today to get a true taste of its elegance and beauty.
